<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Entity: solid_curve_font
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Styled_curve_mim.solid_curve_font">
<note> The local rules for this entity have not been fully updated to agree with the changes in clause 4.2.</note><p>

A <b>solid_curve_font</b> is a  <express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.pre_defined_curve_font"/> that implements the ARM concept
of  <express_ref linkend="Styled_curve:arm:Styled_curve_arm.Solid_curve"/>.
</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: curve_style_font_and_scaling_unique_constraint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Styled_curve_mim.curve_style_font_and_scaling_unique_constraint">
<note> This rule may not have been updated to agree with the changes in clause 4.2.</note><p>

The <b>curve_style_font_and_scaling_unique_constraint</b> rule constrains the  <express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style_font_and_scaling"/> name attribute in a population to satisfy the uniqueness requirement of the ARM application object  <express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style_font_and_scaling"/>.
</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: curve_style_font_and_scaling_unique_constraint.WR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Styled_curve_mim.curve_style_font_and_scaling_unique_constraint.wr:WR1">

The name shall be unique within a population of  <express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style_font_and_scaling"/>.

</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: curve_style_requires_length_measure_with_unit
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Styled_curve_mim.curve_style_requires_length_measure_with_unit">
<note> This rule may not have been updated to agree with the changes in clause 4.2.</note><p>

The <b>curve_style_requires_length_measure_with_unit</b> rule constrains the
entity pointed to by the curve_width attribute of a  <express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style"/>.
</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: curve_style_requires_length_measure_with_unit.WR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Styled_curve_mim.curve_style_requires_length_measure_with_unit.wr:WR1">
A  <express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style"/>.curve_width shall be a  <express_ref linkend="measure_schema:ir_express:measure_schema.length_measure_with_unit"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: curve_style_unique_constraint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Styled_curve_mim.curve_style_unique_constraint">
<note> This rule may not have been updated to agree with the changes in clause 4.2.</note><p>

The <b>curve_style_unique_constraint</b> rule constrains the representation
population members, that fill the role of ARM  <express_ref linkend="presentation_appearance_schema:ir_express:presentation_appearance_schema.curve_style"/>, so that the
ARM name shall be unique within the population.
</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: curve_style_unique_constraint.WR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Styled_curve_mim.curve_style_unique_constraint.wr:WR1">
Every instance of representation with a name of 'curve style parameters' must
have a unique  <express_ref linkend="qualified_measure_schema:ir_express:qualified_measure_schema.descriptive_representation_item"/>.description attribute where the
 <express_ref linkend="qualified_measure_schema:ir_express:qualified_measure_schema.descriptive_representation_item"/> has a name of 'curve style name' and is a member
of the representation's set of items.
</ext_description>

</ext_descriptions>
